name: Over 9000 Neonz!
description:
CuddleofDeath's tribute to the NEONZ Project (created by @Sutuverse).

This creature has the features of a Cyborg Scarecrow, complete with sharp, vampire-like fangs and a cape to conceal the creature's limbs. It is said to be infused with the power of over 9000 Neonz.

This creature may look scary, but it is rumored to bring good luck to those who collect it!
